    "Algorithms for computing the Green function based on variational time evolution and on a Lehmann representation of the spectral function have been developed 156.",
    "A similar approach for magnon spectra has been proposed and tested on IBM quantum computers 157.",
    "Quantum computation of Floquet spectra in periodically driven many-body systems can be enhanced using multi-level qudit quantum computing platforms 158.",
    "These are just a few examples of the many different types of quantum algorithms that have been developed and proposed for DQS.",
    "For an overview of other quantum algorithms we refer to other reviews 54, 159, 160."
